    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Your research into the heart\u2019s development and creation has proven most worthwhile. As you suspected, a millennia of deferred maintenance and caretaking has left the heart in rough shape. Specifically, it seems the heart would not be able to hold a regular beat forever, and so would need to be re-calibrated every so often."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "It\u2019s no small task, but you think that if you deliver to it a powerful enough electric shock, you can stabilize the heart and bring it back into rhythm, thereby saving the arcology and the Valley above."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Gain the"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "CLEAR!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "and"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "THE CAGE CRUMBLES"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "missions. Search the General set for copies of Crimson Guardian equal to the number of Rangers and shuffle them into the path deck."
        }
      ]
    },
